---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Genome Insider.">
  <section class="wrap about-page">
    <span class="eyebrow">About</span>
    <h1 class="about-title">About Genome Insider</h1>

    <div class="prose about-body">
      <p>
        Genome Insider is a collection of explanations, notes, and explorations at the
        intersection of biology, computation, and medicine.
      </p>

      <p>
        Created by <strong><a href="#tanaya">Tanaya Datar</a></strong>, this platform explores bioinformatics,
        molecular biology, immunology, and computational approaches to understanding complex
        biological systems.
      </p>

      <p>
      Genome Insider was designed and built by me using Astro and is deployed with Vercel. The goal was to create a clean, fast, and distraction-free space for exploring biology, genomics, and computational science.
      </p>
      
      <h2 id="tanaya" class="author-title">About the Author</h2>
      <p>
        Tanaya is a computational cancer researcher, with a passion for algorithms, data-driven
        discovery, and decoding the complexity of biological systems through code. Outside of
        coding, she enjoys writing articles about science and watching sitcoms. Tanaya aspires
        to revolutionize cancer treatment and become the CEO of a biopharmaceutical company one day.
      </p>

      <div class="social-links">
        <a 
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/tanaya-datar-7484b62b5/" 
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          💼 LinkedIn
        </a>

        <a 
          href="https://github.com/tanaya2026" 
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          💻 GitHub
        </a>
      </div>

       <h2 id="tanaya" class="author-title"></h2>

    </div>

    <hr class="rule" />

    <div class="about-cta">
      <a href="/articles" class="btn">Read the articles</a>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-ghost">Get in touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    max-width: 720px;
    padding-block: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
  }

  .about-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    margin: 0.3rem 0 1.75rem;
  }

  .about-body p:first-child {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  #tanaya {
    scroll-margin-top: 100px;
  }

  .social-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .social-links a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .social-links a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .about-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
</style>